{"node_id": "c4986b36c89252269f99632332a4f0c1", "title": "Function inputs & outputs: equation", "description": "Find all the inputs that correspond to a given function output, using the function's formula.", "topic_path": ["Khan Academy (English - US curriculum)", "Math by grade", "High school", "Integrated math 1", "Functions", "Inputs and outputs of a function", "Function inputs & outputs: equation"], "assessment_items": [{"item_id": "48b0ae69749052aeb4357dfd5856dd57", "question_content": "$f(t) = -2t+5$\n\n$f\\Big($ [[☃ input-number 1]]$\\Big)=13$", "hints": ["We need to solve an equation with the function's formula $-2t+5$ on one side and the given output $13$ on the other side.", "$\\begin{align}\n-2t+5&=13\\\\\\\\\n-8&=2t\\\\\\\\\n-4&=t\n\\end{align}$\n\n**Therefore, $f(-4)=13$.**"], "widget_types": ["input-number"], "answer_data": {"input-number 1": {"type": "input-number", "value": -4, "answerType": "number", "simplify": "required", "inexact": false, "maxError": 0.1}}}, {"item_id": "8ce95a19367b52e4986bce98eca989f6", "question_content": "$g(x) = 2x+9$\n\n$g\\Big($ [[☃ input-number 1]]$\\Big)=15$", "hints": ["We need to solve an equation with the function's formula $2x+9$ on one side and the given output $15$ on the other side.", "$\\begin{align}\n2x+9&=15\\\\\\\\\n2x&=6\\\\\\\\\nx&=3\\end{align}$\n\n**Therefore, $g(3)=15$.**"], "widget_types": ["input-number"], "answer_data": {"input-number 1": {"type": "input-number", "value": 3, "answerType": "number", "simplify": "required", "inexact": false, "maxError": 0.1}}}, {"item_id": "796dda0ff052570690d54403b3ea231a", "question_content": "$g(t) = 6t-1$\n\n$g\\Big($ [[☃ input-number 1]]$\\Big)=-7$", "hints": ["We need to solve an equation with the function's formula $6t-1$ on one side and the given output $-7$ on the other side.", "$\\begin{align}\n6t-1&=-7\\\\\\\\\n6t&=-6\\\\\\\\\nt&=-1\\end{align}$\n\n**Therefore, $g(-1)=-7$.**"], "widget_types": ["input-number"], "answer_data": {"input-number 1": {"type": "input-number", "value": -1, "answerType": "number", "simplify": "required", "inexact": false, "maxError": 0.1}}}, {"item_id": "85ec0d53b24c50b78f46b3e7c1607b19", "question_content": "$h(x) = 8x-10$\n\n$h\\Big($ [[☃ input-number 1]]$\\Big)=62$", "hints": ["We need to solve an equation with the function's formula $8x-10$ on one side and the given output $62$ on the other side.", "$\\begin{align}\n8x-10&=62\\\\\\\\\n8x&=72\\\\\\\\\nx&=9\\end{align}$\n\n**Therefore, $h(9)=62$.**"], "widget_types": ["input-number"], "answer_data": {"input-number 1": {"type": "input-number", "value": 9, "answerType": "number", "simplify": "required", "inexact": false, "maxError": 0.1}}}, {"item_id": "bf3d65a406f35d118c3a7b77e83efe26", "question_content": "$h(t) = -10t+6$\n\n$h\\Big($ [[☃ input-number 1]]$\\Big)=-44$", "hints": ["We need to solve an equation with the function's formula $-10t+6$ on one side and the given output $-44$ on the other side.", "$\\begin{align}\n-10t+6&=-44\\\\\\\\\n50&=10t\\\\\\\\\n5&=t\\end{align}$\n\n**Therefore, $h(5)=-44$.**"], "widget_types": ["input-number"], "answer_data": {"input-number 1": {"type": "input-number", "value": 5, "answerType": "number", "simplify": "required", "inexact": false, "maxError": 0.1}}}, {"item_id": "2f1498b806885159a47a1a785f5a3f3f", "question_content": "$h(t) = 4t+20$\n\n$h\\Big($ [[☃ input-number 1]]$\\Big)=4$", "hints": ["We need to solve an equation with the function's formula $4t+20$ on one side and the given output $4$ on the other side.", "$\\begin{align}\n4t+20&=4\\\\\\\\\n4t&=-16\\\\\\\\\nt&=-4\\end{align}$\n\n**Therefore, $h(-4)=4$.**"], "widget_types": ["input-number"], "answer_data": {"input-number 1": {"type": "input-number", "value": -4, "answerType": "number", "simplify": "required", "inexact": false, "maxError": 0.1}}}, {"item_id": "9edf2fe78ae159e09fc60c8b1d61c190", "question_content": "$f(x) = -7x-1$\n\n$f\\Big($ [[☃ input-number 1]]$\\Big)=-8$", "hints": ["We need to solve an equation with the function's formula $-7x